<L>__{interior queen's private quarters night}
<A>__{on elizabeth imperfectly reflected in a mirror in the soft candlelight. her ladies are putting her clothes away. bess begins the process of stripping away her make up. lizabeth studies her true face as it comes into view.}
<C>__{elizabeth}
<D>__{lines round my mouth. where did they come from?}
<C>__{bess}
<D>__{smile lines, my lady.}
<C>__{elizabeth}
<D>__{smile lines? when do i smile?}
<A>__{with that she smiles, and sees bess's answering reflected smile.}
<C>__{elizabeth}
<D>__{now you have smile lines too.}
<A>__{her smile fades. she gazes at her now naked face, vulnerable in the mirror.}
